body:
Dear Valued User,

We've detected unusual activity on your account. For your safety, we have temporarily suspended it.
Please verify your identity immediately by clicking here: http://microsft-login-portal.com/verify

Failure to do so within 24 hours will result in permanent account closure.

Sincerely,
The Microsoft Security Team

Hi Team,

Just a friendly reminder that open enrollment for benefits ends next Friday. Please make sure to log into the employee portal to review your options and make your selections.

If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to reach out to the HR department.

Best,
Zenith Corp HR

Your package with tracking number #8102395492 could not be delivered due to an incorrect address.

Please update your shipping information to schedule a new delivery attempt: https://bit.ly/fedex-update-address

A small redelivery fee may apply.

Thank you,
FedEx Customer Support

Hello,

Here's your weekly roundup of the top stories in tech:

- AI Startup 'NexusMind' raises $50M in Series B funding.
- The latest advancements in quantum computing.
- Review: The new flagship smartphone from Orbit.

Read more on our website.

Thanks for reading,
TechCrunch

Hi Mark,

Following up on our call, please find the attached invoice for last month's services. Let me know if you have any questions.

The document is password protected for security. Please use the secure portal to view it: http://secure-document-viewer.io/inv8347

Best,
Jane Doe

URGENT SECURITY ALERT: A new device has been registered to your online banking account.

If this was NOT you, please click this link IMMEDIATELY to secure your account: http://your-bank-security-check.com/auth

Reference ID: 882-AX4

Sincerely,
Your Bank Security Dept.

Hi there,

You have a new direct message from Sarah Connor in the 'Project Skynet' workspace.

You can view the message by logging into Slack.

Cheers,
The Slack Team

Action Required: Your Office 365 password is set to expire in 1 day.

To maintain access to your email and documents, you must update your password now.

Please use the following link to keep your current password: [http://office365-password-renewal.info]

Thank you,
IT Administration

Dear Customer,

We noticed a login to your account from an unrecognized device in Moscow, Russia.

IP Address: 89.108.77.1
Time: 03:15 UTC

If this was you, you can ignore this email. If this was not you, please follow the steps on our resolution center to secure your account.

Sincerely,
PayPal

Congratulations! You've been selected to receive a $100 Amazon Gift Card!

To claim your reward, simply complete this short survey about your shopping experience.

Claim your gift card now: [http://bit.ly/amazon-winner-100]

This is a limited-time offer, so act fast!

Sincerely,
Amazon Promotions

Hi,

Here's your invoice from 'Innovate Solutions Inc'.
Amount Due: $1,450.00
Due Date: 15/10/2023

You can view and pay the invoice online through our secure portal.

Thanks for your business,
Innovate Solutions Inc (via QuickBooks)

Hi,

I'm in a meeting right now and need you to do something for me urgently. Can you purchase ten $100 Amazon gift cards for some clients?

Scratch off the back and send me the codes via email as soon as you have them. I will reimburse you first thing tomorrow.

This is very important.

Thanks,
[CEO's Name]

Hi team,

We will be performing scheduled maintenance on the company VPN this Saturday from 2 AM to 4 AM EST. During this time, access to internal network resources will be unavailable.

No action is required from your end. We apologize for any inconvenience.

Thank you,
IT Department

There's a problem with your billing information.

We were unable to process your last payment. To keep your subscription active, please update your payment details.

Update Payment Info: [http://netflix-account-settings.tv/login]

We're here to help if you need it.

-The Netflix Team

Hi,

This is a confirmation that your password for your Google Account has been changed.

If you did not change your password, your account may have been compromised. Please follow the steps at our account recovery page to secure your account.

Sincerely,
The Google Accounts team

You have received a new document to sign: 'Confidentiality Agreement Q4 2023'.

Please review and sign the document by EOD today.

REVIEW DOCUMENT: [http://docusign-secure-portal.net/view/doc=98234]

Thank you,
DocuSign

Invitation: Marketing Sync @ Wed Oct 11, 2023 10am - 10:30am (your-email@yourcompany.com)

Organizer: marketing-lead@yourcompany.com

Location: Google Meet

Are you going? Yes - Maybe - No

Dear customer, your parcel (ID: 7895-1234) is waiting for you at our depot. Our courier was unable to deliver it to your address.

To reschedule a new delivery, please visit our tracking portal and fill out the form: http://dhl-reschedule-delivery.com

A fee of $1.99 is required for redelivery.

DHL Express

Your Apple ID was used to sign in to iCloud via a web browser.

Date & Time: October 10, 2023, 8:45 PM PDT
Browser: Chrome
Location: Ashburn, VA, USA

If the information above looks familiar, you can disregard this email. If you have not signed in recently and believe someone may have accessed your account, go to iforgot.apple.com to reset your password.

URGENT: Your mailbox is almost full.

Your mailbox is currently at 98% capacity. To avoid losing new emails, you must increase your quota immediately.

Click here to request a quota increase: [http://mail-quota-increase-portal.com]

This is an automated message. Please do not reply.

IT Helpdesk

Official Notification: Tax Refund Pending

Our records indicate that you are eligible for a tax refund of $785.60. Due to a system error, your refund could not be processed automatically.

To receive your refund, you must submit an electronic verification form.

Click here to complete the form: [http://irs-gov-refunds.org/claim]

Please have your Social Security Number and bank details ready.

Internal Revenue Service

John Doe invited you to view the folder "Q4 Marketing Assets".

Go to folder

Enjoy!
The Dropbox team

You have received a new voicemail.

Length: 0:42 seconds
From: +1 (555) 123-4567

To listen to this voicemail, please click the link below and log in to your account:
http://ringcentral-voicemail-access.net/listen?id=9a8b7c

RingCentral

Hello,

Thank you for your order. We'll let you know once your items have shipped.

Order Details
Order #113-9876543-1234567
Arriving:
Thursday, October 12

Your order will be sent to:
John Smith
123 Main St
Anytown, USA

View or manage your order in Your Orders.

Subject: Password Chck Required Immediately

Due to a reent security breach, all employees must reset their pasword immediately.

Click here to update: http://tinyurl.com/companylgn

Your account will be lockd if you do not comply.

Thanks,
IT

For your security, we've disabled withdrawals on your account.

We detected a sign-in from a new IP address (104.28.11.123 - Vietnam). To re-enable withdrawals, please verify your identity by confirming your recent activity.

[Confirm Activity Button linking to a phishing site]

If you don't recognize this activity, please contact support immediately.

Thanks,
The Coinbase Team

Suspicious Activity Detected on Your Account

We have detected suspicious transactions on your Wells Fargo account. For your protection, we have placed a temporary hold on your account.

Please log in to your account to review the transactions and confirm your identity.

Review Activity: [http://wellsfargo-secure-login.net/activity]

If you fail to verify your account, it will be permanently suspended.

Wells Fargo Security

Your flight to Las Vegas is confirmed!

Confirmation #: HJK-LMNP
Flight: Delta 1234
Departs: SFO, Nov 5, 8:00 AM
Arrives: LAS, Nov 5, 9:30 AM

Manage your trip or check-in for your flight on Expedia.com.

Happy travels!
The Expedia Team

Important: Action Required Regarding Your 401(k) Plan

Our 401(k) provider is changing from Fidelity to Vanguard. You are required to log in to the new portal to set up your account and transfer your funds.

Please complete this process by October 31st to avoid any disruption to your contributions.

Access the new portal here: [http://vanguard-employee-portal.com]

Thank you,
Human Resources

Your flight is delayed.

Your American Airlines flight AA456 from DFW to LAX is now scheduled to depart at 4:30 PM.

We apologize for the inconvenience. You can check the latest flight status on our website or mobile app.

American Airlines

Your Zoom meeting recording is now available.

Topic: Q3 Financial Review
Date: Oct 10, 2023

You can view the recording here: [https://zoom.us/rec/play/aBcDeFg...]

Thank you for using Zoom!
The Zoom Team

Unusual Card Activity

We have detected unusual activity on your American Express card ending in 1005. A charge of $1,250.00 at a merchant in Singapore was attempted.

If you do not recognize this charge, please click the link below to dispute it and secure your account.

Dispute Charge: [http://amex-dispute-center.org]

Sincerely,
American Express

Hi Team,

Attached is the revised project plan for Q4. Please review the updated timelines and deliverables.

The file is hosted on our secure SharePoint. You will need to log in to access it.

Access Document: [http://sharepoint-login.live-access.net/project-plan]

Let's discuss this in our sync tomorrow.

Thanks

We want your feedback!

Thank you for being a customer of Innovate Inc. Would you take 2 minutes to complete a short survey about your experience? Your feedback helps us improve.

Start Survey

Thanks,
The Innovate Inc. Team

URGENT: Your domain yourcompany.com is expiring.

Your domain is set to expire in 3 days. To avoid website downtime and loss of your domain, you must renew it immediately.

Renew Now: [http://domain-renewal-services.com/renew?domain=yourcompany.com]

Failure to renew will result in the permanent loss of your domain.

Thank you,
Domain Services

e-Alert: Your available balance is less than $25.00

This is an automated message to inform you that the available balance for your checking account (...1234) is $15.75 as of 10/10/2023 11:30 AM ET.

Log in to Online Banking to view your account details.

Bank of America

Your website's SSL certificate has expired.

The SSL certificate for your-website.com has expired, which may cause security warnings for your visitors.

Please click here to install the new certificate immediately: [http://ssl-install-portal.org/install]

This process is mandatory to keep your website secure.

Technical Support

Hi user,

You've added a new email, user@gmail.com, to your Instagram account.

If this was you, click here to confirm your email address.

If this wasn't you, click here to revert this change.

Thanks,
The Instagram Team

Your latest bill is ready to view

Your AT&T bill for October is now available. Your payment of $85.43 will be automatically deducted on October 20th.

To view your bill details, please visit our secure document viewer: [http://att-bill-viewer.com/view]

Thank you for choosing AT&T.

Need you to do something for me

Hi, I need you to handle a payment for me. Can't talk right now, I'm in a conference.

Let me know if you are available, this is urgent.

Sent from my iPhone

You appeared in 9 searches this week

See who's viewed your profile. Stay connected with your network on LinkedIn.

View Profile

LinkedIn

Mandatory Security Software Update

All employees are required to install a mandatory security update on their computers by the end of the day. This update patches a critical vulnerability.

Please download and run the updater from the link below:

Download Update: [http://company-updater.net/security.exe]

Your machine will be scanned for compliance tomorrow morning.

IT Security

You're running out of space!

Your Dropbox is almost full. Upgrade now to get 2 TB of storage and advanced sharing features.

Upgrade now

The Dropbox Team

FRAUD ALERT: Your Chase account has been locked.

We detected a suspicious login attempt from an IP address in Nigeria. For your security, we have locked your account.

To unlock your account, you must verify your identity.

Verify Here: [http://chase-unlock-account-forms.com]

Thank you for your cooperation.
Chase Bank Security Team

Weekly Digest

Stories for you, based on your reading history.

- The Art of Doing Nothing
- How I Built a SaaS with No Code
- 10 Python Tricks for Data Scientists

Explore more on Medium.

Mailbox De-activation Notice

Your email account has been flagged for unusual activity and is scheduled for de-activation in 48 hours.

If you wish to continue using our service, please verify your account details below to confirm you are the legitimate owner.

VERIFY MY ACCOUNT: [http://email-verification-center.org/login]

Thank you,
Mail Server Administrator

Your family's all here

The members of your Spotify Premium for Family plan have all joined. Now, what to listen to?

Discover new music and podcasts on Spotify.

Happy listening,
Spotify

Your document 'Rental Agreement' has been signed by all parties.

You can now download the completed document.

View Completed Document

Thank you for using DocuSign.

Payment Overdue

Hi,

This is a reminder that invoice #4567 for $2,500 is now overdue. Please process this payment as soon as possible.

The original invoice is attached. For your convenience, you can also view it on our secure portal and pay by credit card: [http://secure-invoice-pay.com/4567]

Regards,
Accounting Department

Your video is live!

Your video "My Trip to the Mountains" has been successfully uploaded and is now public.

You can view it on your channel.

The YouTube Team

Claim Your Lost Luggage

We have found a bag that matches the description of your lost luggage. To confirm ownership and arrange for delivery, please fill out the claim form below.

Claim Form: [http://united-baggage-claim.org/form]

A small verification fee is required.

United Airlines Baggage Services

Hi,

I'm out of the office today but need you to print a document for me from my personal account. The password is 'Password123!'.

Can you log into my Gmail (user@gmail.com) and print the file called "urgent_presentation.pdf"?

Let me know once you have it.

Thanks,
[Your Colleague's Name]

Your prescription is ready for pickup.

Your prescription for LISINOPRIL is ready for pickup at CVS store #1234 located at 123 Main St.

Thank you,
CVS Pharmacy

Problem with your account

We have detected a problem with your Microsoft 365 account. Your account will be closed soon.

Click here to fix the problem: [http://m365-fix-account.com]

Microsoft Corporation

A new sign-in to your Twitter account

We noticed a new sign-in to your account @username from Chrome on Windows near San Francisco, CA.

Was this you? If so, you can ignore this. If not, please change your password to secure your account.

The Twitter Team
each generated with similar logic and variety...]

Your Geek Squad protection plan is expiring.

Don't leave your devices unprotected. Your plan for 'Samsung 55" TV' is set to expire on October 25, 2023.

Renew your plan today to continue your coverage.

Renew Now

Best Buy

Your iCloud Storage is full.

Your iCloud storage is full. You will not be able to back up your devices or upload new photos and videos until you free up space or upgrade your plan.

To prevent data loss, please upgrade your storage plan now.

Upgrade Storage: [http://icloud-storage-upgrade.com/login]

Apple Inc.

Your Wednesday morning trip with Uber

Thanks for riding with Uber. We hope you enjoyed your trip.

Total: $12.54
Charged to Visa **** 5678

Rate or tip your driver.

Uber

Job Opportunity: Senior Software Engineer at Innovatech

Hi, based on your profile, you seem like a great fit for a Senior Software Engineer role at Innovatech. They are looking for someone with your skills in Python and AWS.

If you're interested, you can view the job description and apply using our "Easy Apply" feature here: [link to a fake linkedin-style site]

This is a great opportunity to join a fast-growing company.

Best regards,
Recruiting Services

Your pizza is on its way!

Your order from Domino's is out for delivery. Your driver, Mike, should be there shortly.

Track your order live on the Domino's Pizza Tracker.

Enjoy your meal!
Domino's

Action Required: Your AWS account is suspended.

Your Amazon Web Services account has been suspended due to a billing issue. We were unable to charge the credit card on file.

To reactivate your account, please update your payment information immediately.

Update Payment: [http://aws-billing-update-portal.net]

All running instances will be terminated if the issue is not resolved within 24 hours.

Amazon Web Services

Prices have dropped for flights to Hawaii!

Good news! The price for your watched flight from SFO to HNL has dropped. Book now before prices go up again.

View Deals

Happy travels,
Kayak

Your Adobe Creative Cloud subscription has been cancelled.

We were unable to process your monthly payment. Your access to all Adobe apps will be revoked.

To reactivate your subscription, please update your billing details on our secure server.

Update Billing: [http://adobe-account-reactivate.com]

Thank you,
The Adobe Team

Your order has shipped!

Good news! Your order from 'HandmadeCraftsShop' has shipped. You can track your package using the tracking number provided on the order details page.

View Order

Thanks for shopping on Etsy!

Dear customer, we are updating our security system. As part of this update, you are required to confirm your account details. Please click the link below and follow the instructions.
http://yourbank.security-update.xyz/confirm
This is a mandatory step to ensure the safety of your funds.
Thank you, Your Bank.

Happy Monday! Just a reminder about our new Fall class schedule starting this week. We've added Yoga at 6 PM on Tuesdays and a new HIIT class on Thursdays at 7 AM. Check the full schedule on our website and book your spot! See you at the gym.

As per our new remote work policy, you are required to log your work hours in the new 'TimeTrack' portal. Your login details are the same as your network credentials. Please ensure your hours for this week are logged by EOD Friday. Portal Link: [https://timetrack.yourcompany.com]

We've detected a suspicious transaction of $542.19 on your card at an international merchant. For your protection, we've put a temporary hold on your card. Please verify this transaction immediately at: http://capitalone.resolve-issue.net to unlock your card.

You are invited to an online meeting titled 'Urgent Project Review'. The meeting starts in 15 minutes. Click the link to join: http://webex-meeting-join.biz/m/12345. You may be prompted to install a browser extension for a better experience.
Hi Team, I'm having trouble accessing the Q4 report on the shared drive. Can someone please send me a direct link or a copy? I need it for the board meeting this afternoon. Thanks, Sarah.

A package is waiting for you. We were unable to deliver your parcel. The shipping label was damaged. Please provide your details and a small redelivery fee of $2.95 to have it resent. Schedule redelivery here: http://usps.redelivery-form.com

Only one week left to get your early bird ticket for TechCon 2024! Join industry leaders for three days of networking, workshops, and groundbreaking announcements. Register now and save $200! Visit our official website: [https://www.techcon2024.com]

Hi, I'm stuck in back-to-back meetings. Can you please handle an urgent invoice payment for me? It's for a new vendor and needs to be paid today. I can't access my banking app. Please text me on my personal WhatsApp at +1-555-123-9876 for the details. This is time-sensitive. Regards, David Chen, CFO
You have new ideas for your 'Home Decor' board! We've found 15 new Pins we think you'll love. Come see what's new.

MANDATORY SECURITY TRAINING: All employees must complete the mandatory 2023 Cybersecurity Awareness training by this Friday. Failure to comply will result in suspension of network access. Begin your training here: http://corp-security-training.net/start
Hi user, We've just released a new feature: Advanced Reporting! Now you can get deeper insights into your data. Log in to your dashboard to check it out. Let us know what you think!

Subject: Your investment portfolio requires attention.
Dear client, based on recent market shifts, I recommend rebalancing your portfolio. Please log in to our secure portal to review my detailed suggestions and approve the proposed trades.
Link: http://wellsfargo-investments-portal.com
Regards, Your Financial Advisor
Your package from 'GadgetStore' is scheduled for delivery tomorrow, October 11th. You can manage your delivery preferences or track the package on our website.

Dear member, your subscription is expiring. We were unable to authorize the payment. To continue enjoying your favorite shows, please update your payment method. Update here: http://netflix.update-billing.org. Thank you, Netflix Team.

Reminder: The annual employee performance review cycle is now open. Please log in to the HR portal to complete your self-assessment by October 20th. Your manager will then schedule a meeting to discuss. Any questions, please contact HR.

You have been sent a secure legal document via 'SecureDocs'. This document requires your immediate review and electronic signature. Please access the document using the link below with your company credentials. Access Link: http://legaldocs.secure-file.net/s/8f7d6e
Severe Weather Alert for your area. A thunderstorm warning is in effect until 8:00 PM. Expect heavy rain and strong winds. Stay safe and informed.

Your Apple ID has been locked for security reasons. We have detected unauthorized sign-in attempts. To unlock it, you must verify your identity. Please visit: http://appleid.verify-now.com. If you do not verify within 24 hours, your account will be permanently disabled.
Your audience is growing! You've had 50 new subscribers this week. Keep up the great work! Log in to view your detailed report.

Hi, I need a list of all employee mobile numbers for an urgent broadcast via a new alert system we're testing. Please compile it in an Excel sheet and upload it to this secure folder by 2 PM. This is confidential. Link: http://acme-files.net/upload/secure. Thanks, [CEO's Assistant Name]
Your order from 'The Burger Joint' is being prepared. It should be ready for pickup in about 15-20 minutes. We'll notify you when it's on the way.

Open Enrollment is Here! It's time to choose your benefits for the upcoming year. Please review the updated plan documents and make your selections in the benefits portal before the deadline. Portal: http://yourcompany.benefits-enroll.com. Your login is your employee ID.
Your electricity bill is ready. Your auto-payment for $123.45 is scheduled for October 15th. No action is needed. You can view the detailed bill on our website.

You have a $50 reward certificate waiting for you! As a valued member, we'd like to thank you for your loyalty. Claim your reward by logging into your account here: http://costco.claim-reward.org. This offer expires soon!
[RepoName] A new pull request has been opened by 'user_x'. Please review the changes and merge if they are acceptable. You can view the PR here: [link to github.com]

A critical vulnerability has been identified in the VMware product you are using. It is imperative that you apply the patch immediately to prevent unauthorized access. Download the patch from our security bulletin: http://vmware-security.patch-download.com/bulletin-8574
A new donation has been made to your fundraiser 'Help Save the Local Library'! Someone just donated $50. Thank you for making a difference.

Important message regarding your account. We have updated our Cardmember Agreement. No action is required from you, but you can review the full updated agreement on our website. Thank you for being an American Express Card Member.

Our mail server is undergoing an upgrade. To ensure you do not lose any emails, please log in to your account through the migration portal to validate your mailbox. Validation Link: http://my-company-mail-migration.com. This must be completed by 5 PM today.
Your morning news briefing is here. Top stories: - City council approves new downtown development. - Local sports team wins championship. - Weather forecast: sunny with a high of 75°F.

You are due a tax refund of £345.80 from HMRC. To claim your refund, please fill out the online form with your details. Click here to proceed: http://hmrc.claim-refund-online.net. Please have your bank details ready.
Project Update: Task 'Finalize Q4 Budget' has been assigned to you by John Smith. The due date is this Friday, October 13th. View task in Asana.

Someone has your password. Someone just used your password to try to sign in to your Google Account. Google blocked them, but you should check what happened. Check activity here: http://accounts.google.verify-access.org
It's time to check in for your flight. Your flight to Seattle (SEA) departs in 24 hours. Check in now to get your boarding pass.

You have a new voicemail message (2:15 min) from your CEO's office.
To listen to the message, please access your secure mailbox using the link below. You will be asked to authenticate.
Access Voicemail: http://cisco.voicemail-portal.com/listen/msg=123
Your new bill is available. Amount due: $69.99. Due Date: 10/25/2023. You are enrolled in automatic payments, so no action is required. Thank you for being a customer.

A new document 'Q4 Performance Review - CONFIDENTIAL' has been shared with you by HR. Please review and provide your feedback by tomorrow. Access the document here: http://sharepoint.corporate-login.net/docs/834
Your reservation is confirmed. You're all set for a table for 2 at 'The Italian Place' this Friday at 7:30 PM. We look forward to seeing you!
Your statement is ready. Your September checking account statement is now available to view online. Log in to your Wells Fargo account to view it.

Your password for yourcompany.com expires today. Please use the following temporary password 'Temp12345' to log in and create a new one. Login Portal: http://mail.your-organization.com. If you fail to do so, please contact the helpdesk tomorrow to reactivate your account.

Your Online Banking has been suspended. This is due to a failed security check. To restore access, you must re-verify your account information. Click here to begin: http://bankofamerica.reactivate-online.com
Did you know you can create videos in Canva? Bring your designs to life with our easy-to-use video editor. Animate text, add stock footage, and create stunning videos in minutes. Try it now!

You have received a document for signature from your CEO. The document is 'Urgent M&A Agreement'. Please sign before 12:00 PM today.
Sign Document: http://adobesign.secure-portal.org/sign/1
You have a new message! Someone is interested in getting to know you. Log in to your Match.com account to read the message and reply.

Withdrawal Initiated. A withdrawal of 1.5 BTC has been initiated from your account. If this was NOT you, please cancel the transaction immediately by clicking the link below.
Cancel Transaction: http://gemini.cancel-transfer.net
Your moment of Calm. Take a deep breath. Let it out. Ready for today's 10-minute daily meditation? Let's begin.

Helpdesk Ticket #7895 has been closed. Your issue regarding 'Cannot connect to printer' has been resolved. If you are still experiencing problems, please reopen the ticket or contact the helpdesk. The solution was to restart the print spooler service on your machine.

You missed a meeting. A meeting titled 'Quarterly Planning' was held today and you were marked as absent. You can view the meeting recording and a transcript of the discussion here: http://zoom.us.view-recording.com/play/9876

u/user123 replied to your comment in r/askreddit.
'That's a great point, I never thought of it that way!'
See the full comment thread.

Hi, I need you to process a wire transfer for me to a new vendor. The amount is $15,200. I'm in a meeting and can't provide the details over email. Text my personal cell at 555-867-5309 for the wire information. This needs to be done in the next hour. Thanks, [Executive Name]

New sign-in from an unrecognized device. We detected a new sign-in to your Google Workspace account from a Linux device in Frankfurt, Germany. If this was not you, please secure your account immediately by changing your password. If this was you, you can ignore this alert.

Your Antivirus Subscription Has Expired! Your computer is now vulnerable to viruses and malware. Renew your subscription immediately to stay protected. Get 50% off if you renew today! RENEW NOW: http://mcafee.renew-subscription.net

Your upcoming trip to Paris. Just a reminder, your stay at 'Charming apartment near Eiffel Tower' begins in 3 days. Check your itinerary for check-in instructions and contact information for your host.

Hi, this is Mark from IT. We're troubleshooting a network issue that seems to be originating from your account. I need you to tell me your password so I can log in as you and run some diagnostics. I'll let you know when I'm done so you can change it back. Please reply with your current password.
Card 'Design new homepage mockups' was moved to 'In Review' on board 'Website Redesign' by Jane Doe. View the board to see the latest progress.

Action Required: Update Your Direct Deposit Info. Due to a system upgrade, all employees must re-enter their direct deposit information in the new payroll portal to ensure you receive your next paycheck on time.
Update Here: http://payroll.portal-update.com/login

We tried to deliver your package today at 2:15 PM, but no one was available. You can schedule a new delivery or choose to pick it up at a nearby FedEx location. Manage your delivery: [link to fedex.com]
Invoice from 'Local Coffee Shop'. Due: $4.50. Thank you for your business! You can view and pay your invoice here: [link to squareup.com]

VPN Access Re-authentication Required. To enhance security, we are requiring all users to re-authenticate their VPN credentials. Please connect to the VPN, then visit the following internal site to complete the process: http://10.0.1.5/vpn-reauth. This must be done today.

Security Alert: Your LastPass master password was used to log in from a new device in Brazil. If this was not you, please click here to lock your account and reset your master password immediately: http://lastpass.secure-reset.com/lock
Your flight to Denver is now boarding. This is the final boarding call for flight WN1234 to Denver (DEN) at gate B5.

Several failed login attempts were detected for your account. We have temporarily blocked access. To unblock, please verify your recent activity by signing in at our security center: http://microsoft.login-activity.com. This link will expire in one hour.
You have a new friend request. John Smith wants to be your friend. You have 10 mutual friends. Confirm or Ignore.
The fire alarm test is scheduled for this Friday at 11:00 AM. The alarm will sound for approximately 60 seconds. No evacuation is necessary. Thank you for your cooperation.

Your site has been compromised! Our security scan has detected malware on your WordPress website. Immediate action is required to clean the site and prevent blacklisting by search engines. Click here for our professional removal service: http://wordpress.security-cleanup.net
